# Chronypt Backend + Onboarding ‚Äî Implementation Plan

Build a Node.js + Express backend with dual-database architecture (PostgreSQL + MongoDB), user authentication, OAuth social logins, and a 4-step premium onboarding wizard for new users.

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Frontend
        A[React App] --> B[Login / Sign Up]
        B --> C[Onboarding Wizard]
        C --> D[Dashboard]
    end
    subgraph Backend
