```

| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| API Server | Node.js + Express | REST API, routing, middleware |
| Auth | Passport.js + JWT | Local auth + OAuth strategies |
| PostgreSQL | Prisma ORM | Users, profiles, onboarding data |
| MongoDB | Mongoose | Sessions, activity logs |
| Validation | Zod | Request body validation |
| Security | bcrypt, helmet, cors | Password hashing, HTTP security |

